snippet.title: BLOCnog iOS Trailer Gameplay
snippet.description:
BLOCnog, already available on Apple TV is coming soon to your iOS devices. To ALL iOS devices running 9.1 or later!

more details at http://www.gameshot.org/BLOCnog and https://www.facebook.com/BLOCnog
